text: 3.5 stars. Toast and coffee ok. We drop by after our bike ride. Friendly staff. I suspect the workflow a bit messy. Got a few breakfast wrong. Price is reasonable.

It sounds like they might be struggling to balance their expenses with the quality of their offerings. Perhaps they could consider reevaluating their pricing strategy to better reflect the taste and experience they provide.
The atmosphere is great here with the live band, good place to chill but not good for dining, food is salty , bad and expensive
Nice drinks and very welcoming ! Thank you !

Chill atmosphere. If you're looking for something away from the bustling city crowd, this is a place to go.

Employees are friendly, and happy to serve. @Yoyo thank you for the positive experience.
